_ ``me and my girl,'' jim dale stars in the 1930s english musical hit about a cockney scamp making it big in high society. marquis, 382-0100. teletron. ticketron. available
_ ``oba oba,'' a brazilian dance revue. now in previews, opens march 29. ambassador, 239-6200, same number as telecharge. available
